WEBVTT

00:00:16.216 --> 00:00:19.019
[ARES] Onwards! The time is
now, my valiant soldiers!

00:00:19.119 --> 00:00:24.691
[ARES] Let the indomitable
Kingdom of Rakia strike fear
into the hearts of Orario's
adventurers!

00:00:24.791 --> 00:00:28.595
(SOLDIERS rally &amp; cheer)

00:00:43.710 --> 00:00:46.880
[MESSENGER 1] Sir, the First,
Second, and Third Cavalry have
all been destroyed!

00:00:46.980 --> 00:00:50.684
[MESSENGER 2] (panicked panting)
They've also wiped out twelve
infantry units! They're all
gone!

00:00:50.784 --> 00:00:54.454
[MESSENGER 2] Literally
everyone on the battlefield
has been obliterated!

00:00:54.555 --> 00:00:55.421
(MARIUS groan)

00:00:55.522 --> 00:00:58.559
[ARES] What the hell? Seriously?

00:00:58.659 --> 00:01:01.628
[ARES] Why?!

