[AISHA] Take care of yourself.

00:01:05.666 --> 00:01:10.303
Miss Aisha, thank you
for everything. I am
indebted to you.

00:01:10.403 --> 00:01:12.438
If you hadn't done what you did
who knows what would have happ‐

00:01:12.539 --> 00:01:14.541
Please, Haruhime.
Don't get sappy.

00:01:14.641 --> 00:01:17.778
I was only following
my impulsive nature.

00:01:18.979 --> 00:01:21.114
What are your
plans now?

00:01:21.214 --> 00:01:22.716
[AISHA] Excellent question.

00:01:22.816 --> 00:01:25.886
[AISHA] The Kingdom of Rakia has
set up camp outside the city.

00:01:25.986 --> 00:01:27.453
[AISHA] I might
pay them a visit.

00:01:27.554 --> 00:01:29.623
[HARUHIME] The Kingdom of
Rakia...?

00:01:29.723 --> 00:01:30.824
[WELF] The Ares Familia.

00:01:30.924 --> 00:01:32.793
[WELF] Their monstrous army
is launching an attack

00:01:32.893 --> 00:01:35.061
on Orario as we speak...

00:01:35.161 --> 00:01:37.197
[WELF] Luckily, they're
all sizzle, no steak.

00:01:37.297 --> 00:01:39.766
[WELF] They might number
in the thousands...

00:01:39.866 --> 00:01:43.036
but ordinary soldiers are no
match for seasoned adventurers.

00:01:43.136 --> 00:01:47.340
[HESTIA] What a pain in the
butt. Ares is totally stuck
in the Dark Ages.

00:01:47.440 --> 00:01:48.809
[BELL] So... we're under attack?

00:01:48.909 --> 00:01:51.411
[AISHA] Well, doesn't matter
whether they win or lose..

00:01:51.512 --> 00:01:55.181
[AISHA] As long as there
are men, my girls and I
have a job to do.

00:01:56.416 --> 00:01:58.218
Don't tell me it
still bothers you.

00:01:58.318 --> 00:01:59.520
You do realize that you‐ Oh?

00:01:59.620 --> 00:02:02.322
[LENA] Aisha! We
should get going soon!

00:02:02.422 --> 00:02:04.558
[AISHA] I know.
Give me a moment.

00:02:04.658 --> 00:02:11.164
[AISHA] Anyway, Haruhime, you're
free now. Live your life however
you see fit. Okay, Darling?

00:02:11.264 --> 00:02:13.834
[HARUHIME] I will.

00:02:13.934 --> 00:02:17.037
And it better not get back to me
that you're treating her poorly,
Cranel.

00:02:17.137 --> 00:02:21.007
[BELL] Huh?!
[AISHA] If anything happens
to my little Renard, your ass
will be mine.

00:02:21.107 --> 00:02:22.809
(HESTIA stewing)
[BELL] R‐right!

00:02:23.877 --> 00:02:25.045
(AISHA giggle)

00:02:25.145 --> 00:02:26.780
Ta‐ta!

00:02:31.084 --> 00:02:32.619
So, how did it go?

00:02:32.719 --> 00:02:34.621
I wanna hear how she took
it when you told her

00:02:34.721 --> 00:02:36.723
she never actually accomplished
her nightly duties.

00:02:36.823 --> 00:02:39.459
Right? The poor little
thing would always faint

00:02:39.560 --> 00:02:41.461
before the main event.
You told her didn't you?

00:02:41.562 --> 00:02:45.398
Eh, why bother. I don't see the
point in bringing it up now.

00:02:45.498 --> 00:02:50.771
[AISHA] It seems they've already
moved past all that... whether
she's done something or not.

00:02:51.538 --> 00:02:57.310
[OPENING SONG, "HELLO to DREAM"]

00:04:25.733 --> 00:04:28.636
[HERMES] Oh very good! Sounds
like it all worked out then.

00:04:28.736 --> 00:04:33.308
[HERMES] And Haruhime has
joined the Hestia Familia?

00:04:33.408 --> 00:04:35.175
[HERMES] Mm. I'm
relieved to hear that.

00:04:35.276 --> 00:04:37.312
[BELL] Well, we have you to
thank, Master Hermes.

00:04:37.412 --> 00:04:40.448
I really appreciate you telling
me about the Killing Stone.

00:04:40.548 --> 00:04:44.184
Don't thank me. I'm just
a guy with a big mouth.

00:04:45.520 --> 00:04:47.822
You're the one who saved the
damsel in distress.

00:04:47.922 --> 00:04:49.357
Great job, hero.

00:04:49.457 --> 00:04:54.695
I just reacted. I wanted to
help her in any way possible.

00:04:54.795 --> 00:04:57.965
So tell me... Are you familiar
with the Three Great Quests?

00:04:58.065 --> 00:04:58.833
[BELL] The what...?

00:04:58.933 --> 00:05:00.335
[HERMES] Heh. Right.

00:05:00.435 --> 00:05:02.870
Basically the world's been
waiting for a legendary hero.

00:05:02.970 --> 00:05:05.172
Pretty similar to
how Haruhime was.

00:05:05.273 --> 00:05:10.611
Long has the world watched,
looking towards Orario to
fulfill its deepest desire.

00:05:10.711 --> 00:05:12.179
Hence "Three Great Quests".

00:05:12.280 --> 00:05:14.482
They call for the extermination
of three ancient monsters

00:05:14.582 --> 00:05:16.617
that emerged from
the Dungeon long ago.

00:05:16.717 --> 00:05:21.055
[HERMES] Behemoth, the King
of the Land. Leviathan,
the Lord of the Sea.

00:05:21.155 --> 00:05:26.160
[HERMES] Now, these two
monsters already lay slain
at the hands of the strongest
Familias in existence.

00:05:26.261 --> 00:05:28.996
[BELL] Are you referring
to Miss Ais and the others?

00:05:29.096 --> 00:05:31.832
[BELL] The Loki Familia
and the Freya Familia?

00:05:31.932 --> 00:05:33.568
[HERMES] Nope, not them.

00:05:33.668 --> 00:05:36.170
[HERMES] Who I'm talking about
are the Zeus and Hera Familias.

00:05:36.271 --> 00:05:39.674
[HERMES] They were formerly
hailed as the most powerful
in the history of Orario.

00:05:39.774 --> 00:05:43.177
[HERMES] They combined their
strength in order to challenge
the third monster.

00:05:43.278 --> 00:05:45.680
However.. they were wiped out.

00:05:45.780 --> 00:05:49.584
(BELL shock)
[HERMES] The third monster is
called "The Black Dragon."

00:05:49.684 --> 00:05:51.886
Wait, do you mean... the
one‐eyed beast from

00:05:51.986 --> 00:05:56.257
Dungeon Oratoria? I think
I might know what you are
talking about.

00:05:56.357 --> 00:06:00.194
[BELL] It's the darkest shade
of black anyone's ever seen.

00:06:00.295 --> 00:06:02.162
[BELL] And its wings are
the absence of light.

00:06:02.263 --> 00:06:07.268
[BELL] It's a walking
nightmare... A living legend...
A herald of death...

00:06:07.368 --> 00:06:13.274
It isn't a fairy tale.
The Black Dragon is lurking
somewhere and is a real threat.

00:06:13.374 --> 00:06:16.043
[HERMES] The Three Great Quests
have yet to be completed...

00:06:16.143 --> 00:06:17.978
(BELL serious)

00:06:18.078 --> 00:06:20.248
[HERMES] And the
world wants a hero.

00:06:21.282 --> 00:06:22.883
And remember Bell...

00:06:22.983 --> 00:06:26.887
This responsibility falls
on the shoulders of Orario's
adventurers.

00:06:26.987 --> 00:06:28.222
[BELL] Right.

00:06:28.323 --> 00:06:30.291
[ARES] How is this possible...?!

00:06:30.391 --> 00:06:34.228
I demand to know how they could
trounce my army like it's
absolutely nothing!

00:06:34.329 --> 00:06:36.030
[MARIUS] Oh that's easy.

00:06:36.130 --> 00:06:39.634
[MARIUS] We severely
underestimated how strong
Orario's adventurers are.

00:06:39.734 --> 00:06:43.271
They're wiping the floor
with us. At this rate they'll
take us all prisoner.

00:06:43.371 --> 00:06:45.573
[MARIUS] Let's just
pack it up and go home.

00:06:45.673 --> 00:06:48.909
We honestly had no
business starting a war
in the first place.

00:06:49.009 --> 00:06:50.210
(ARES frustrated)

00:06:51.078 --> 00:06:52.347
[ARES] Cease your foolishness.

00:06:52.447 --> 00:06:54.249
Such impudence is inexcusable!

00:06:54.349 --> 00:06:57.852
[ARES] Your father, Martinus,
has never had a problem
following my orders!

00:06:57.952 --> 00:07:00.788
[MARIUS] There's a reason
why they call my father the
King of the Pushovers,

00:07:00.888 --> 00:07:03.724
it's because he indulges
your idiotic blathering!

00:07:03.824 --> 00:07:06.827
[ARES] Hm? (nervous)
You dare speak to a
god that way, Marius?!

00:07:06.927 --> 00:07:09.264
[MARIUS] I'm just calling it
like I see it, numbskull!

00:07:09.364 --> 00:07:14.602
[ARES] I'm not a numbskull!
Only a numbskull would call
a numbskull a numbskull.
You numbskull.

00:07:19.340 --> 00:07:21.909
(HARUHIME "whew" sigh)

00:07:23.444 --> 00:07:24.779
[BELL] I'm back, Miss Haruhime.

00:07:24.879 --> 00:07:27.748
[HARUHIME] Hello! Welcome
home, Master Bell.

00:07:27.848 --> 00:07:32.587
[BELL] Woah, doing laundry for
six must be tough! Let me give
you a hand with that.

00:07:32.687 --> 00:07:34.422
[HARUHIME] Y‐you mustn't,
Master Bell!

00:07:34.522 --> 00:07:36.156
It's fine. I'm happy
to help out.

00:07:36.257 --> 00:07:38.293
[HARUHIME] No, that's not what
I'm referring to.

00:07:38.393 --> 00:07:39.694
Don't worry about it.

00:07:39.794 --> 00:07:40.928
No wait stop!

00:07:42.096 --> 00:07:43.431
[BELL] Eek!

00:07:44.499 --> 00:07:46.601
[HESTIA] Oh, sorry, am I
interrupting something?

00:07:46.701 --> 00:07:49.270
What exactly are the two of
you smiling about down there?

00:07:49.370 --> 00:07:50.805
[HARUHIME] Lady Hestia?!
[BELL] G‐Goddess!

00:07:50.905 --> 00:07:53.541
(BELL nervous)

00:07:53.641 --> 00:07:55.310
[HESTIA] I've made a decision.

00:07:55.410 --> 00:07:57.878
From now on, physical contact
with the opposite sex

00:07:57.978 --> 00:08:00.415
is strictly prohibited
within my Familia. Got it?

00:08:00.515 --> 00:08:02.283
[BELL] Huh?
[HARUHIME] Wait, what?

00:08:02.917 --> 00:08:04.018
[HESTIA] Am I clear?

00:08:04.118 --> 00:08:06.186
[BELL &amp; HARUHIME] (fear) Y‐yes..

00:08:06.287 --> 00:08:08.389
(HARUHIME nervous)

00:08:10.725 --> 00:08:12.427
[HESTIA] That includes
your dumb tail!

00:08:12.527 --> 00:08:14.895
[HARUHIME] (startled)
I‐I'm sorry!

00:08:14.995 --> 00:08:16.431
[LILI] This is abuse of power!

00:08:16.531 --> 00:08:18.699
[LILI] Not letting us have any
physical contact is going

00:08:18.799 --> 00:08:21.436
to have a negative effect on
our activities in the Dungeon!

00:08:21.536 --> 00:08:23.070
[HESTIA] Sounds like
a personal problem!

00:08:23.170 --> 00:08:25.806
You're a smart cookie though,
I bet you'll figure it out!

00:08:25.906 --> 00:08:27.242
It'll be impossible!

00:08:27.342 --> 00:08:29.944
I assume the same rule
applies to you too, right?

00:08:30.044 --> 00:08:32.880
So there will be no
more touching Master
Bell from now on.

00:08:32.980 --> 00:08:34.782
I'm the goddess of this Familia!

00:08:34.882 --> 00:08:38.052
If I can't touch him, then
how in the hell am I supposed
to update his status?!

00:08:38.152 --> 00:08:40.455
[LILI] Sounds like
a personal problem!
What the hell
caused all this?

00:08:40.555 --> 00:08:42.590
[LILI] You're a smart
cookie, blah, blah, blah.
I'm sorry to say this
is all my fault...

00:08:42.690 --> 00:08:44.925
Stop being such a stupid head!

00:08:45.025 --> 00:08:46.294
I'm a stupid head?!

00:08:46.394 --> 00:08:48.763
[HESTIA LILI] (anger) Hmph!

00:08:48.863 --> 00:08:52.967
Fine! In the event touching
is necessary... no flirting
is allowed!

00:08:53.067 --> 00:08:57.972
Indecent behavior comes from
a lewd mind... So any obscene
conduct is unacceptable!

00:08:58.072 --> 00:09:00.341
[LILI] The only obscene thing
here is your outfit!

00:09:00.441 --> 00:09:02.243
Don't speak to a virgin
goddess that way!

00:09:02.343 --> 00:09:07.382
One question. If we can't
associate with the opposite
sex... then, uh...

00:09:07.482 --> 00:09:10.084
[MIKOTO] Does that...
apply to gods as well?

00:09:10.184 --> 00:09:11.519
[HESTIA] Hm?

00:09:11.619 --> 00:09:13.721
[WELF] Actually... I was
wondering the same thing...

00:09:13.821 --> 00:09:18.793
I'm kinda... uh, good friends
with Lady Hephaistos, so, uh...

00:09:18.893 --> 00:09:19.494
[BELL] Oh?

00:09:19.594 --> 00:09:21.462
(HESTIA evil giggle)

00:09:21.562 --> 00:09:23.264
That's totally fine!

00:09:23.364 --> 00:09:26.567
I wholeheartedly welcome
feelings of love between
gods and their children!

00:09:26.667 --> 00:09:28.969
[HESTIA] It's a dream of mine
to see our romance blossom,

00:09:29.069 --> 00:09:33.641
just as it did between Spirits
and our children before we
descended from Heaven!

00:09:34.842 --> 00:09:36.977
How do you feel
about it, Bell?

00:09:37.077 --> 00:09:37.978
[BELL] Wait, what?

00:09:38.078 --> 00:09:39.146
Are you kidding me?!

00:09:39.247 --> 00:09:40.748
I see through your shenanigans.

00:09:40.848 --> 00:09:42.950
Holding gods to a different
standard is unfair!

00:09:43.050 --> 00:09:44.084
(HESTIA pained)

00:09:44.184 --> 00:09:45.453
Fine, then! Do
whatever you want...

00:09:45.553 --> 00:09:47.555
I really couldn't care less!

00:09:49.790 --> 00:09:51.959
So, Bell... hypothetically...

00:09:52.059 --> 00:09:56.331
Let's say there's this beautiful
goddess, and one day she admits
her feelings for you...

00:09:56.431 --> 00:09:57.898
[HESTIA] How would you reply?

00:09:57.998 --> 00:09:59.500
(LILI nervous)

00:10:01.369 --> 00:10:03.137
Oh... I'd turn her down.

00:10:03.238 --> 00:10:07.308
(HESTIA mortified) (wilting)

00:10:07.408 --> 00:10:09.244
It'd never happen anyway.

00:10:09.344 --> 00:10:11.612
Besides, even if a
goddess did ask me out...

00:10:11.712 --> 00:10:13.348
I couldn't imagine dating one.

00:10:13.448 --> 00:10:15.215
[BELL] It'd be way
too intimidating.

00:10:15.316 --> 00:10:16.684
(HESTIA defeated)

00:10:16.784 --> 00:10:19.754
[LILI] Uh‐Lady Hestia...?
[HESTIA] Bell, you...

00:10:19.854 --> 00:10:26.627
[HESTIA] Big Jerk!
[BELL] Huh?

00:10:27.495 --> 00:10:29.997
[WELF] Think we'll
see her again?

00:10:30.097 --> 00:10:32.700
I have a feeling she won't
be back for a while.

00:10:32.800 --> 00:10:33.634
(BELL gasp)

00:10:33.734 --> 00:10:35.836
[BELL] Goddess!
Why did she...?!

00:10:35.936 --> 00:10:37.772
[WELF] You kind of
had that coming, Bell.

00:10:37.872 --> 00:10:40.775
[BELL] Huh?!
[MIKOTO] You did word
it a little harshly.

00:10:40.875 --> 00:10:44.912
[BELL] But... the gods are Gods!
We're supposed to respect them!

00:10:46.180 --> 00:10:48.048
(uncomfortable) So then...

00:10:48.148 --> 00:10:51.519
does that same exact logic
apply... if you're talking

00:10:51.619 --> 00:10:54.922
about the relationship between
adventurers and supporters?

00:10:55.022 --> 00:10:56.391
[BELL] Huh?

00:10:56.491 --> 00:10:58.526
If you refused to give someone
a chance just because

00:10:58.626 --> 00:11:01.362
they came from a different
background than you...

00:11:01.462 --> 00:11:05.966
[LILI] ...don't you think
that would probably hurt
their feelings pretty badly?

00:11:15.510 --> 00:11:18.846
[BELL] I'm going to
go look for her!

