00:11:49.744 --> 00:11:52.513
[AISHA] Tsk... Not a
decent one among them...

00:11:52.613 --> 00:11:55.182
I should've expected as much
from a bunch of grunts...

00:11:55.283 --> 00:12:00.321
[SAMIRA] Aisha! Some fresh meat
just rolled in over that way.
Let's take advantage!

00:12:00.421 --> 00:12:03.391
Huh? Great... be right there!

00:12:03.491 --> 00:12:04.825
I've made a decision!

00:12:04.925 --> 00:12:06.361
[ARES] Given the circumstances,

00:12:06.461 --> 00:12:08.195
I shall journey
to Orario myself!

00:12:08.296 --> 00:12:10.598
[MARIUS] What? You plan on
sightseeing or something?

00:12:10.698 --> 00:12:12.333
Don't be an idiot!

00:12:12.433 --> 00:12:13.768
In order to turn the tide...

00:12:13.868 --> 00:12:16.103
I'm planning on abducting
one of their local Gods!

00:12:16.203 --> 00:12:18.673
[ARES] I'll kidnap them...
No, I'll "god‐nap" them!

00:12:18.773 --> 00:12:21.609
And then, I'll force those
Orario nitwits to surrender!

00:12:21.709 --> 00:12:22.543
(MARIUS in disbelief)

00:12:22.643 --> 00:12:24.245
Oh my freakin' me!

00:12:24.345 --> 00:12:25.980
My new plan is foolproof!

00:12:26.080 --> 00:12:27.181
[MARIUS] Are you crazy?!

00:12:27.282 --> 00:12:29.417
How exactly do you plan
on sneaking into Orario?!

00:12:29.517 --> 00:12:33.053
[ARES] Make haste, Marius!
Assemble a group of our
finest men!

00:12:33.153 --> 00:12:36.891
[ARES] Today, we abduct a god,
whomever it may be!

00:12:36.991 --> 00:12:39.727
You haven't even decided
which god you're going for?!

00:12:39.827 --> 00:12:43.264
How big of a hot‐headed
dumbass can you be?!

00:12:43.364 --> 00:12:45.533
[MARIUS] Come back!

00:12:45.633 --> 00:12:47.635
[BOSS] Sorry, honey,
we're fresh out.

00:12:47.735 --> 00:12:49.237
Goddess...

00:12:56.444 --> 00:12:58.613
[BELL] Where could
she have gone...?

00:13:00.881 --> 00:13:02.116
[MIACH] Is that you, Bell?

00:13:02.216 --> 00:13:03.484
(BELL notice)

00:13:03.584 --> 00:13:04.619
Hey there. Been a while.

00:13:04.719 --> 00:13:07.021
Master Miach..
Lady Hephaistos...

00:13:07.121 --> 00:13:09.957
Hey, uh... have either of
you seen my goddess lately?

00:13:10.057 --> 00:13:12.793
Hestia, huh? Hmm...

00:13:12.893 --> 00:13:15.896
I'm sorry, Bell...
I'm afraid I haven't
seen her around.

00:13:15.996 --> 00:13:17.698
Yeah I haven't
seen her either.

00:13:17.798 --> 00:13:23.137
No worries... Well, thank you
anyway... I should get going.

00:13:23.238 --> 00:13:27.074
