00:13:27.174 --> 00:13:28.042
[BELL] Huh?

00:13:28.142 --> 00:13:30.445
Let me guess; you
got into a fight.

00:13:30.545 --> 00:13:32.046
I can see it on your face.

00:13:32.146 --> 00:13:33.914
(BELL hesitation)

00:13:38.719 --> 00:13:41.622
[BELL] I'm not really sure
how it escalated so quickly.

00:13:42.790 --> 00:13:44.592
[BELL] So, uh... Can I
ask you something...

00:13:44.692 --> 00:13:46.627
Has a god or a
goddess ever, y'know...

00:13:46.727 --> 00:13:49.464
fallen in love with someone
from the lower world?

00:13:49.564 --> 00:13:52.667
Would that even...
even be possible?

00:13:52.767 --> 00:13:54.469
(HEPHAISTOS surprised)

00:13:54.569 --> 00:13:55.970
Of course... Yeah
I'm sure of it.

00:13:56.070 --> 00:13:58.273
[BELL] Really?
[MIACH] Honestly speaking...

00:13:58.373 --> 00:14:01.576
we sometimes find ourselves
quite drawn to you children.

00:14:01.676 --> 00:14:02.777
It's true.

00:14:02.877 --> 00:14:05.212
[HEPHAISTOS] Fondness,
a passing fancy,

00:14:05.313 --> 00:14:06.881
motherly or fatherly love...

00:14:06.981 --> 00:14:08.583
[HEPHAISTOS] Our love
takes on many forms,

00:14:08.683 --> 00:14:11.352
but there's no denying
that we have a soft spot
for our children.

00:14:11.452 --> 00:14:15.155
Sometimes.. there may be
feelings of romantic interest.

00:14:15.256 --> 00:14:16.257
(sniff)

00:14:16.357 --> 00:14:17.392
(BELL surprised)

00:14:17.492 --> 00:14:19.527
Um, but, we're
talking about gods

00:14:19.627 --> 00:14:20.895
being with people here!

00:14:20.995 --> 00:14:22.997
We're completely different
from each other.

00:14:23.097 --> 00:14:26.534
Who we are... Our
backgrounds... And even...

00:14:26.634 --> 00:14:28.903
[BELL] How long we live...

00:14:31.739 --> 00:14:34.108
What is it exactly that
you're afraid of, Bell?

00:14:34.208 --> 00:14:35.276
(BELL gasp)

00:14:35.376 --> 00:14:36.877
Y'see.. in our eyes,

00:14:36.977 --> 00:14:39.314
that love lasts a mere moment.

00:14:39.414 --> 00:14:40.881
From our children's
perspective...

00:14:40.981 --> 00:14:44.485
that same love lasts
their entire life.

00:14:44.585 --> 00:14:46.487
[HEPHAISTOS] If you find
yourself being pursued
by a goddess,

00:14:46.587 --> 00:14:48.523
make sure you give
her a proper answer.

00:14:48.623 --> 00:14:54.629
Even if there's someone
else out there you have
feelings for... Got it?

00:14:54.729 --> 00:14:56.997
We aren't suggesting that
you should be intimidated

00:14:57.097 --> 00:15:00.501
by a deity, just speak
honestly and openly.

00:15:00.601 --> 00:15:02.237
That's all you
really have to do.

00:15:02.337 --> 00:15:04.439
[MIACH] I'm sure there are
many gods out there who

00:15:04.539 --> 00:15:07.708
would understand and
accept your answer.

00:15:07.808 --> 00:15:11.045
So... please don't run
away... from a god's love.

00:15:11.145 --> 00:15:14.415
[MIACH] Turn them down
gracefully or take them
up on the offer.

00:15:14.515 --> 00:15:16.717
Just... don't be afraid.

00:15:17.485 --> 00:15:19.720
(HESTIA inhale)

00:15:20.555 --> 00:15:22.290
[HESTIA] Bell, you big jerk!

00:15:22.390 --> 00:15:26.193
[HESTIA] You spineless,
pig‐headed, stubborn little
hare brain doofus!

00:15:26.294 --> 00:15:30.331
[HESTIA] Why does he
respect us gods so much
in the first place?!

00:15:30.431 --> 00:15:33.133
On one hand, I'm happy that
he thinks so highly of me...

00:15:33.233 --> 00:15:35.536
but he doesn't have to
be so uptight about it!

00:15:35.636 --> 00:15:36.771
[BOSS] Hestia!
[HESTIA] Hmm?

00:15:36.871 --> 00:15:38.038
[BOSS] Perfect timing!

00:15:38.138 --> 00:15:40.174
[HESTIA] Potato Popper
Boss Lady!

00:15:40.275 --> 00:15:43.611
[HESTIA] Okay... So why
exactly do I have to be put on

00:15:43.711 --> 00:15:47.382
digging duty for the Potato
Poppers? Can't you see I'm
of slight stature?

00:15:47.482 --> 00:15:50.851
I'm very busy! You know I
can't keep customers waiting!

00:15:50.951 --> 00:15:53.521
I won't be able to keep up with
demand with just the one sack.

00:15:53.621 --> 00:15:57.492
[BOSS] I'm going to need another
big bag for the cart over on
Main Street.

00:15:57.592 --> 00:15:58.993
(HESTIA annoyed sigh)
[BOSS] Alright, I'll
leave you to it!

00:15:59.093 --> 00:16:00.361
[HESTIA] Huh?! But Boss‐!

00:16:00.461 --> 00:16:01.462
[BOSS] Thank you!

00:16:01.562 --> 00:16:03.498
Dangit... I'm a god, you know!

00:16:03.598 --> 00:16:09.003
Hmph. Doesn't she realize I
can't just leave Orario whenever
I feel like it...?

00:16:10.538 --> 00:16:13.207
(thundering)
[HESTIA] Great, it looks like
it's about to rain...

00:16:14.108 --> 00:16:15.476
But I suppose
it'd be pretty hard

00:16:15.576 --> 00:16:18.479
to make Potato Poppers without
the main ingredient...

00:16:21.549 --> 00:16:22.483
[GANESHA] Hey, hold it!

00:16:22.583 --> 00:16:23.384
(HESTIA startled)

00:16:23.484 --> 00:16:25.052
Hmm...? Wait, Hestia?

00:16:25.152 --> 00:16:26.487
Ganesha!

00:16:31.326 --> 00:16:34.562
Whatcha say, Marius?! Isn't
this a splendid disguise?!

00:16:34.662 --> 00:16:39.233
Keep your voice down! Besides,
It's not much of a disguise!
All you did was put on a cloak!

00:16:39.334 --> 00:16:41.902
Anyway... what exactly
is your plan now?

00:16:42.002 --> 00:16:44.004
[ARES] It's quite simple really:

00:16:44.104 --> 00:16:46.574
We locate a suitable target
inside the city walls,

00:16:46.674 --> 00:16:48.776
seize them, and bring
them back with us!

00:16:48.876 --> 00:16:50.511
[MARIUS] That's all
you came up with?!

00:16:50.611 --> 00:16:53.814
[MARIUS] Just how
stupid are you?!

00:16:53.914 --> 00:16:55.383
[HESTIA] Thanks a
lot, Ganesha...

00:16:55.483 --> 00:16:57.685
I really appreciate you letting
me sneak through the gate.

00:16:57.785 --> 00:17:02.122
Of course... Potato Poppers
enrich our city and the
lives of its citizens!

00:17:02.222 --> 00:17:08.095
Let no man nor noble god...
deny you permission to gather
potatoes for the greater good!

00:17:08.463 --> 00:17:09.464
I am...

00:17:11.098 --> 00:17:13.301
...Ganesha! (agh)

00:17:13.401 --> 00:17:16.571
I can't believe I have
to go deliver potatoes.

00:17:16.671 --> 00:17:18.739
[ARES] Hmm?
[HESTIA] Huh?

00:17:18.839 --> 00:17:19.874
[ARES] Hestia?

00:17:19.974 --> 00:17:21.442
[HESTIA] Ares?

00:17:21.542 --> 00:17:23.344
(ARES wild laughter)

00:17:24.712 --> 00:17:27.348
(HESTIA screaming)

00:17:27.448 --> 00:17:28.649
Gotcha!

00:17:28.749 --> 00:17:29.884
(ARES proud laughter)

00:17:29.984 --> 00:17:31.419
[ARES] Did you see that,
Marius?!

00:17:31.519 --> 00:17:33.888
I've captured a god without
ever setting foot in Orario!

00:17:33.988 --> 00:17:36.391
[ARES] Now you can see the
genius behind my plan!

00:17:36.491 --> 00:17:37.525
[MARIUS] You're a jackass.

00:17:37.625 --> 00:17:38.393
[ARES] Alright, let's go.

00:17:38.493 --> 00:17:39.527
[MARIUS] Huh? Wait!

00:17:42.730 --> 00:17:44.198
(GANESHA confused)

00:17:47.101 --> 00:17:51.239
[BELL] Thanks so much to you
both... I appreciate you taking
the time to talk to me.

00:17:51.339 --> 00:17:54.242
[MIACH] I hope what we said
helps you, if only a little.

00:17:54.342 --> 00:17:57.512
Yes, it helps...
Although, honestly...

00:17:57.612 --> 00:18:00.147
[BELL] I'm still not quite
sure what I should do.

00:18:00.248 --> 00:18:03.518
You can start by finding
Hestia. You should patch
things up first.

00:18:03.618 --> 00:18:05.052
[BELL] Right!

00:18:09.324 --> 00:18:12.593
I wonder if maybe she's headed
back to the mansion already.

00:18:13.261 --> 00:18:14.295
(BELL notice)

00:18:16.631 --> 00:18:17.432
[BELL] Miss Ais!

00:18:17.532 --> 00:18:18.966
(AIS notice)

00:18:20.067 --> 00:18:21.201
[AIS] Come with us.

00:18:21.302 --> 00:18:22.237
[BELL] Huh?

00:18:23.003 --> 00:18:24.672
[LOKI] That shrimp, I swear...

00:18:24.772 --> 00:18:26.607
Always such a pain in my ass...

00:18:26.707 --> 00:18:27.742
[AIS] Loki! Finn!

00:18:27.842 --> 00:18:28.876
(LOKI FINN notice)

00:18:30.278 --> 00:18:32.613
[BELL] (catch breath) Hey!
Is it true that my Goddess...

00:18:32.713 --> 00:18:33.914
she was kidnapped?!

00:18:34.014 --> 00:18:36.016
Yeah... unfortunately
it's true.

00:18:36.116 --> 00:18:40.288
It's all thanks to a certain
masked idiot, lettin'
her waltz out the gate!

00:18:40.388 --> 00:18:41.689
I am Ganesha...!

00:18:41.789 --> 00:18:44.692
I don't wanna hear another
word outta you, ya moron!

00:18:44.792 --> 00:18:46.427
I am Ganesh‐! (kicked)

00:18:46.527 --> 00:18:48.463
[LOKI] Shut your face!

00:18:48.563 --> 00:18:50.298
No.. my Hestia..

00:18:50.398 --> 00:18:52.132
Finn.. Any word
from the party?

00:18:52.232 --> 00:18:54.902
[FINN] Not yet. The enemy
forces have split off

00:18:55.002 --> 00:18:57.071
into several groups moving
in different directions.

00:18:57.171 --> 00:19:01.676
And that means... we don't know
who to follow since we don't
know who has the little runt.

00:19:01.776 --> 00:19:05.280
Plus, we gotta chase 'em through
the mountains, so we better
hurry or we'll lose 'em.

00:19:05.380 --> 00:19:07.548
[FINN] I'm a bit
embarrassed to admit it,

00:19:07.648 --> 00:19:11.286
[FINN] but they're likely more
familiar with the terrain
outside of Orario than we are.

00:19:11.386 --> 00:19:12.753
(BELL discouraged)

00:19:12.853 --> 00:19:14.555
[AIS] I'm going out there.
[BELL] Huh?

00:19:14.655 --> 00:19:16.023
[LOKI] Hold up, Aisy‐poo!

00:19:16.123 --> 00:19:17.191
You don't have ta
go outta your way for

00:19:17.292 --> 00:19:18.526
the annoying little half‐pint!

00:19:18.626 --> 00:19:21.596
[AIS] But... someone
has to chase after her.

00:19:22.430 --> 00:19:23.464
Very well, Ais...

00:19:23.564 --> 00:19:25.533
We'll leave it to you.

00:19:25.633 --> 00:19:27.067
I... I'm going too!

00:19:27.167 --> 00:19:30.104
Come on... Were you even
listening to me, Bell?

00:19:30.204 --> 00:19:33.408
Ais told us she's got
this. You're just gonna
get her the way.

00:19:33.508 --> 00:19:34.875
(BELL shock)

00:19:34.975 --> 00:19:36.411
But she's my goddess!

00:19:36.511 --> 00:19:40.981
She's my responsibility!
So please... let me go too!

00:19:41.081 --> 00:19:45.052
[LOKI] (annoyed) Fine, whatever.

00:19:45.152 --> 00:19:47.488
But... if we chase
the target blindly,

00:19:47.588 --> 00:19:49.324
the culprits might escape.

00:19:49.424 --> 00:19:53.294
If we could just narrow
down which one of their groups
has Lady Hestia...

00:19:53.394 --> 00:19:55.696
[HERMES] I think I may
be of assistance!

00:19:55.796 --> 00:19:57.865
[BELL] Huh? Master Hermes!

00:19:57.965 --> 00:20:00.200
You just need to know
where Hestia is, right?

00:20:00.301 --> 00:20:01.902
Can you help with that?

00:20:02.002 --> 00:20:05.940
Sure... I've got...
"Persius," Asfi at my side!

00:20:06.040 --> 00:20:07.608
(embarrassment)

00:20:10.378 --> 00:20:14.214
(BELL panting)

00:20:20.988 --> 00:20:23.291
[BELL, internal] Goddess...
Please be okay!

00:20:27.928 --> 00:20:29.029
[BELL] Miss Ais...?

00:20:29.129 --> 00:20:30.097
[AIS] Hurry.

00:20:30.197 --> 00:20:32.300
[BELL] R‐right!

00:20:32.400 --> 00:20:34.302
You dummy! Let me
down right now!

00:20:34.402 --> 00:20:37.071
You have another think
coming if you think
you'll get away with this!

00:20:37.171 --> 00:20:39.106
(quick laugh) I already
have you bimbo!

00:20:39.206 --> 00:20:41.141
[ARES] You may be
an annoying pipsqueak,

00:20:41.242 --> 00:20:43.878
but you're essential
to our god‐napping plan!

00:20:43.978 --> 00:20:46.481
[HESTIA] Oh! Who are you
calling a pipsqueak?!

00:20:46.581 --> 00:20:49.016
(MARIUS confused)

00:20:50.351 --> 00:20:51.919
[SOLDIER] It‐it's
the Sword Princess!

00:20:52.019 --> 00:20:53.254
(SOLDIERS alert, confusion)

00:20:55.423 --> 00:20:57.458
[HESTIA] Ooh it's
Wallen‐whats‐her‐face!

00:20:57.558 --> 00:21:02.363
[MARIUS] (react) Since
when has Orario been
able master the sky?!

00:21:03.431 --> 00:21:07.034
This rests in your hands,
Sword Princess.

00:21:07.802 --> 00:21:09.570
[ARES] (frustrated) Very well!

00:21:09.670 --> 00:21:12.473
One measly adventurer
isn't enough to stop me!
(HESTIA nervous) (screams)

00:21:12.573 --> 00:21:15.643
I am Ares, patron god of
the Kingdom of Rakia!

00:21:15.743 --> 00:21:20.080
I am the God of War...
Bear witness to my sword!

00:21:20.581 --> 00:21:21.882
(ARES shock)

00:21:21.982 --> 00:21:22.817
(HESTIA struggling)

00:21:22.917 --> 00:21:24.585
(screams) Uh, not bad!

00:21:24.685 --> 00:21:27.522
Do you even know what
the hell you're doing?

00:21:27.622 --> 00:21:28.556
(AIS tense)

00:21:29.123 --> 00:21:30.491
Sword Princess!

00:21:31.926 --> 00:21:33.227
(ASFI caught)

00:21:33.328 --> 00:21:35.763
[MARIUS] Archers,
take aim at that woman!

00:21:35.863 --> 00:21:39.500
[MARIUS] If we capture her,
Orario's adventurers won't
be able to follow us!

00:21:39.600 --> 00:21:42.770
Hey, Marius! Don't give orders
like you're in charge!

00:21:42.870 --> 00:21:44.305
(HESTIA struggling) (surprised)
[ARES] I am the god here!

00:21:44.405 --> 00:21:46.206
Give it a rest!
I'm telling you

00:21:46.307 --> 00:21:48.343
we need to use this chance
and make our retreat!

00:21:48.443 --> 00:21:50.245
[MARIUS] You thick‐headed
donkey!

00:21:50.911 --> 00:21:52.079
[BELL] Goddess!

00:21:52.179 --> 00:21:53.248
[HESTIA] You came, Bell!

00:21:53.348 --> 00:21:56.451
(HESTIA trip) (losing balance)

00:21:56.551 --> 00:21:57.318
[HESTIA] Bell!

00:21:57.418 --> 00:21:58.586
No‐!

00:22:01.822 --> 00:22:03.658
(BELL grabbing hold)

00:22:04.091 --> 00:22:04.892
(AIS effort)

00:22:04.992 --> 00:22:05.960
(SOLDIERS confused)

00:22:06.060 --> 00:22:08.396
[ASFI] Princess! Bell Cranel!

00:22:14.969 --> 00:22:21.709
[CLOSING SONG,
"Sasayaka na Shukusai"]

00:23:45.726 --> 00:23:48.829
[HESTIA] Next time:
"A Song of Love."

